{"tid":1945544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美航母「羅斯福號」25官兵確診　停泊關島消毒檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-27T06:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:39:14.000Z","uid":42762,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2c69a2091f09a980187d2da881b2c0eba4c1c0be","tid":1945544,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"美航母「羅斯福號」25官兵確診　停泊關島消毒檢疫 <br />\n<br />\n美國國防部周四（26日）公布，航母「羅斯福號」確診感染新型冠狀病毒的人員增加，但沒透露確診者人數。美國有線電視新聞網絡（CNN）則引述美國海軍消息稱，艦上確診者已達25名。<br />\n美國海軍作戰部長吉爾代（Michael Gilday）上將表示，羅斯福號目前已停泊在關島進行消毒，全艦官兵僅限在碼頭檢疫，不會進入社區，其他人也不得靠近，吉爾代強調現時無人病情嚴重。<br />\n美國海軍代理部長莫德利（Thomas Modly）指出，羅斯福號約有5000名官兵，已安排為艦上所有人進行病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n（CNN/中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200327/s00005/1585285731726/美航母「羅斯福號」25官兵確診-停泊關島消毒檢疫\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200327%2Fs00005%2F1585285731726%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A6%8F%E8%99%9F%E3%80%8D25%E5%AE%98%E5%85%B5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%8A%E9%97%9C%E5%B3%B6%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f0a5dcc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200327%2Fs00005%2F1585285731726%2F%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E6%AF%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%A6%8F%E8%99%9F%E3%80%8D25%E5%AE%98%E5%85%B5%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E5%81%9C%E6%B3%8A%E9%97%9C%E5%B3%B6%E6%B6%88%E6%AF%92%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB&h=75eb51c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200327/s00005/1585285731726/美航母「羅斯福號」25官兵確診-停泊關島消毒檢疫</a>"},{"pid":"4478ac99c1b34872261cecdac1d3eba580658540","tid":1945544,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"中共化武，無處不在"},{"pid":"6e2b226329db6383edb9b3d4e0cdd666c9cfedfb","tid":1945544,"uid":152589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2